const FAQS = [
  { q: "How much does a custom piece cost?", a: "Custom pieces start from ₹15,000 for simple pendants and earrings. Engagement rings typically range from ₹30,000–₹3 lakh depending on stone size and complexity. We work with your budget honestly and transparently from the first consultation." },
  { q: "Can I supply my own stones or existing gold?", a: "Absolutely. We regularly incorporate customer-supplied diamonds, heirloom gems and existing gold into new designs. This is one of the most meaningful ways to honour family jewellery." },
  { q: "How long does the full process take?", a: "From first consultation to delivery, most custom pieces take 3–6 weeks. Simple pendants and studs can be completed in 2 weeks. Complex engagement ring commissions with rare stones may take up to 8 weeks." },
  { q: "What if I don't know what I want?", a: "That's exactly what our design consultants are for. Bring in photos you like, magazine cutouts, Pinterest boards or just a feeling — we're experienced at translating vague ideas into precise, beautiful designs." },
  { q: "Can I get a custom piece made as a surprise gift?", a: "Yes! We work with many clients creating surprise engagement rings and anniversary gifts. We can consult discreetly, use ring sizing techniques that don't require the recipient, and arrange surprise delivery." },
  { q: "Is the piece truly one of a kind?", a: "Yes. Every Sundaram Jewels custom piece is a single unique creation. We never produce a second piece from your design without your explicit permission. Your design files are held on file for your exclusive future use." },
];

